PLEASURE IS A STATE OF MIND | PLEASURE IS A STATE OF MINE ✨

And what MORE THAN A PLEASURE it was working on this incredible tour assisting my brother @jemelmcwilliams in choreography! Working and learning under your direction only gets better & better! I’m forever grateful! 💪🏾💙 And to @thegreenstone for showing up when and how you do is never taken lightly! Love you always 🪨💚

A HUGE shoutout to the beautiful dance artists & muses @ashabfranklin @callherhelen @biancamuscatelli @cappin.c!! Y’all truly embodied everything “The Age of Pleasure” represents and more! Love y’all to pieces! 😍🫶🏾

The biggest THANK YOU to the iconic @janellemonae for not only sharing and providing a safe haven creatively, professionally, and personally for us all involved but to the entire world to experience as well! GOD’S WORK ☝🏾🙏🏾❤️

And to everyone else involved in the tour + @wondaland family, working/being in you alls orbit regularly filled my cup to the brim and I’ll forever cherish the times! May the Age of Pleasure live on til the end of time! 🙌🏾✨

A Legendary performance with @johnlegend on @nbcthevoice last night singing “What Christmas Means To Me”! Definitely had the folks up on their feet, as a legendary coach would! 🎁💫

Thank you @jemelmcwilliams for yet another magical opportunity! Being able to not only assist you on this but break out the dancing shoes & perform as well was definitely a great Christmas gift in itself! I don’t take experiencing your leadership, expertise, and creative magic for granted! 💪🏾✨

BIG LOVE always to my fellow dance artists and cast members. Sharing space with you all in rehearsals and on the stage was nothing short of amazing! And thank you @meishh @cleartalentgroup for always making sure all things are covered! 🙏🏾❤️

One thing about me …

Choreographed for the ICONIC @mariahcarey at @abudhabievents #saadiyatnights! 🤩🙌🏾

The biggest THANK YOU to choreographer @domkelley for bringing me in as an associate choreographer and trusting me to hold the team down out in Abu Dhabi! Words can’t express my gratitude friend! And @cedricdodd_ for your amazing support and incredible teamwork throughout the entire process as well! It’s a lock for sure! 🔒💪🏾

And of course, a huge SHOUT OUT to the extremely talented cast of dance artist involved @asielhardison @pierrepyer @raymondbaynard @bernardlbell @cedricreboya @markusshields! Working with you all was the best. Great memories were made and I’m looking forward to many more in the future! 👊🏾✨
